<HEAD>Homeless Man Accused of Killing Pigeons Over Peanuts</HEAD>
<DATELINE>RALEIGH, N.C. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A homeless man killed seven pigeons for the
peanuts passersby had thrown the birds, authorities say.
   ``If a pigeon got to a nut first, he would grab the bird and
wring its neck,'' said police Lt. R.C. Friese.
   Passersby near the state Capitol complained to police Sunday
