<HEAD>With AM-Poland Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WARSAW, Poland (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here is a breakdown of the membership of
the Senate and Sejm, the two chambers of Poland's National Assembly:
   SENATE _ 100 members, all freely elected: 98 Solidarity; 1
nonparty, considered pro-Communist, 1 vacancy because of the death
of a Solidarity senator.
