proportional strength set in advance: 173 (37 percent) Communist
Party; 161 (35 percent) Solidarity, 76 (17 percent) United Peasant
Party, 27 (6 percent) Democratic Party, 23 (5 percent) pro-Communist
Christian groups.
   The last group includes PAX with 10 seats, Christian Social Union
with 8 and the Polish Catholic Social Union, 5.
